These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  fisherman, firefighter, engineer, bartender, doctor, pilot, librarian
There are 7 different nationalities: dutch, malaysian, indonesian, polish, spanish, indian, german
 1. the bartender is on the left of the polish##1
 2. the spanish is the bartender##1
 3. the librarian is on the right of the pilot##1
 4. the indonesian is on the right of the indian##1
 5. the engineer is in the middle##1
 6. the dutch is on the far left##1
 7. the doctor is the dutch##1
 8. the fisherman is on the right of the indian##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the malaysian##1
10. the polish is on the left of the engineer##1
11. the librarian is on the right of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | doctor | bartender | firefighter | engineer | fisherman | pilot | librarian |
| Nationality   | dutch    | spanish   | polish      | indian | indonesian    | malaysian    | german         |

