.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: tomato, pomegranate, strawberry, asparagus, cauliflower, orange, kiwi
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: hip-hop, ambient, disco, indie, reggae, house, metal
 1. the fan of reggae is the person eating asparagus##1
 2. the person eating orange is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 3. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 5. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 6. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
 7. the fan of reggae is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
10. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | tomato | pomegranate | cauliflower | asparagus | orange | kiwi | strawberry |
| Music-Genre   | ambient      | disco   | indie   | reggae      | hip-hop       | metal       | house     |

