.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: peach, watermelon, grapes, peas, strawberry, pineapple, zucchini
The people have 7 different jobs:  musician, dancer, electrician, paramedic, manager, fisherman, architect
 1. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 2. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the architect##1
 3. the dancer is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
 4. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
 5. the musician is the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the electrician is on the right of the dancer##1
 7. the dancer is on the left of the electrician##1
 8. the dancer is on the right of the paramedic##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is the paramedic##1
10. the person eating grapes is on the right of the musician##1
11. the paramedic is in the middle##1
12. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | watermelon | strawberry     | grapes  | pineapple       | peach       | zucchini  | peas   |
| Job    | fisherman  | musician | architect | paramedic | dancer | electrician | manager |

