.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: reggae, gospel, salsa, electronic, d&b, techno, blues
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, american, french, colombian, mexican, polish, spanish
 1. the fan of d&b is the american##1
 2. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 3. the polish is on the right of the french##1
 4. the pakistani is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 6. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
 7. the french is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 8. the fan of salsa is on the right of the polish##1
 9. the fan of salsa is the mexican##1
10. the mexican is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
11. the spanish is the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | blues     | electronic     | salsa      | gospel | d&b      | reggae     |
| Nationality   | colombian | french | polish | mexican | spanish | american | pakistani |

