.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, dancing, hiking, card-games, skydiving, puzzles, reading
7 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, rabbit, pony, bird, chinchilla, mouse
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | dancing | hiking | puzzles     | card-games | reading | skydiving | singing |
| Pet     | mouse   | rabbit    | bird | chinchilla     | lizard         | pony     | rat        |

