.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, mirinda, tea, cola, lemonade, milk
The people use 7 different means of transport: taxi, car, subway, train, motorbike, helicopter, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the taxi##1
 3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | lemonade   | hot-chocolate | tea | milk  | cola | water |
| Transport   | train   | motorbike | taxi | helicopter     | car | snowmobile | subway   |

