.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: fantasy, action, disaster, superhero, comedy, musical, romance
The people use 7 different means of transport: van, ship, tram, car, helicopter, bike, taxi
 1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the person watching romance movies is the person driving the car##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 7. the person driving the van is the person watching disaster movies##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
10. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | romance | superhero | comedy | musical     | action | disaster |
| Transport     | bike | car      | taxi | tram    | helicopter | ship   | van  |

